text: Muziekweb () is the website of Muziekwebplein, formerly Centrale Discotheek Rotterdam (Central Music Library of Rotterdam). The website gives access to the library's collection.Centrale Discotheek Rotterdam at Ensie website (12 January 2017) .Warmerdam, Ria (April–June 2012). "Biggest CD collection in Europe now available in streaming format." in Fontes Artis Musicae. Vol. 59, No. 2. pp. 190ff. .
